<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 10:08:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>巴基斯坦选举委员会告诉参议院，2月8日的投票不能推迟</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/resolution-to-delay-february-8-polls-in-pakistan-senate-islamabad-news/articleshow/106861970.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106861970.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦选举委员会拒绝参议院寻求推迟大选的决议，称所有安排均已完成。委员会已发布加强安全并为和平选举创造适宜环境的指示。现阶段不建议推迟选举。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 09:24:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/resolution-to-delay-february-8-polls-in-pakistan-senate-islamabad-news/articleshow/106861970.cms</guid></item><item><title>土耳其士兵在伊拉克阵亡后因“赞扬恐怖主义”而拘留了18人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/turkey-holds-18-people-for-praising-terrorism-after-soldiers-killed-in-iraq/articleshow/106861606.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106861606.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;当局周一表示，上周杀害士兵后，土耳其警方以“赞扬恐怖主义”为由拘留了 18 人，而一名被取缔的库尔德工人党 (PKK) 高级成员在伊拉克北部被“消灭”。周五，九名土耳其士兵在伊拉克北部与库尔德工人党的冲突中丧生，促使安卡拉在伊拉克北部和叙利亚北部进行空袭和行动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 09:09:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/turkey-holds-18-people-for-praising-terrorism-after-soldiers-killed-in-iraq/articleshow/106861606.cms</guid></item><item><title>2023年以色列对外货物贸易下降</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israels-foreign-trade-in-goods-decreased-in-2023/articleshow/106859281.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106859281.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;数据还显示，投资品进口（不包括船舶和飞机）增长了8.0%。然而，与上年相比，钻石（原钻和成品钻石）进口下降29.4%，消费品进口下降1.8%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 07:56:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israels-foreign-trade-in-goods-decreased-in-2023/articleshow/106859281.cms</guid></item><item><title>缅甸叛乱组织声称控制与印度、孟加拉国接壤的城镇</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/myanmar-rebel-group-claims-control-of-town-bordering-india-bangladesh/articleshow/106858773.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106858773.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;若开邦的一个民族武装组织表示，它已经控制了一个与印度和孟加拉国接壤的城镇，这是军政府在与该国多个地区的叛乱作斗争时的最新损失。缅甸在多条战线上正处于叛乱的阵痛之中，在亲民主平行政府支持下的反军政府联盟组织已经控制了多个军事哨所和城镇。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 07:41:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/myanmar-rebel-group-claims-control-of-town-bordering-india-bangladesh/articleshow/106858773.cms</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜为什么要测试高超音速导弹？它们是如何工作的？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/why-is-north-korea-testing-hypersonic-missiles-and-how-do-they-work/articleshow/106857234.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106857234.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;朝鲜领导人金正恩已将高超音速武器的发展列为优先发展军事实力的五年计划的一部分。朝鲜的高超音速导弹试验对其军事能力和地区安全具有多种影响。高超音速武器因其速度、机动性和低空飞行能力而对现有导弹防御系统构成重大挑战。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 07:07:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/why-is-north-korea-testing-hypersonic-missiles-and-how-do-they-work/articleshow/106857234.cms</guid></item><item><title>什么是固体燃料导弹？朝鲜为何要开发它们？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/what-are-solid-fuel-missiles-and-why-is-north-korea-developing-them/articleshow/106856514.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106856514.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;固体燃料导弹是使用预先包装的推进剂混合物的火箭，而不是需要单独的燃料箱和氧化剂的液体燃料导弹。这种看似简单的差异对导弹能力和地缘政治问题都有重大影响。朝鲜正在开发固体燃料导弹，以增强其军事能力并威慑美国及其盟国的潜在威胁。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 06:53:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/what-are-solid-fuel-missiles-and-why-is-north-korea-developing-them/articleshow/106856514.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国官员表示，Covid-19 感染可能在一月份在该国反弹</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinese-officials-say-covid-19-infections-may-rebound-in-country-in-january/articleshow/106856021.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106856021.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;寒假、春节即将到来，卫生部门呼吁及时开展健康咨询转诊、疫苗接种、优化医疗资源和救治流程。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 06:27:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinese-officials-say-covid-19-infections-may-rebound-in-country-in-january/articleshow/106856021.cms</guid></item><item><title>唐纳德·特朗普对共和党政治的控制力在冰冷的爱荷华州党团会议中受到考验</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trumps-grip-on-republican-politics-is-put-to-the-test-in-ice-cold-iowas-caucuses/articleshow/106855203.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106855203.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;投票定于周一晚上在冰冷的爱荷华州开始，特朗普希望取得胜利，这将发出一个响亮的信息：无论是威胁生命的寒冷还是改变生命的法律麻烦都无法减缓他向共和党 2024 年提名迈进的步伐。核心小组参与者将聚集在 1,500 多所学校、教堂和社区中心内讨论他们的选择，有时会持续几个小时，然后进行无记名投票。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 06:05:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trumps-grip-on-republican-politics-is-put-to-the-test-in-ice-cold-iowas-caucuses/articleshow/106855203.cms</guid></item><item><title>台湾当选总统赖清德在代表团访问时赞扬美国的支持</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwans-president-elect-lai-hails-us-support-as-delegation-visits/articleshow/106854800.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106854800.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;赖清德在党部会见代表时表示，自由民主“是台湾人民最宝贵的财富，是保护台湾的圣山”。他说：“这也是台美共同的核心价值观，也是台美伙伴关系长期稳定的基础。”台湾选民不顾北京一再呼吁不要选举赖智的呼吁。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 05:55:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwans-president-elect-lai-hails-us-support-as-delegation-visits/articleshow/106854800.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度裔美国人在美国政治中崛起，掌控身份</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/us-canada-news/indian-americans-rise-in-us-politics-navigate-identity/articleshow/106854535.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106854535.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在今年美国总统候选人之间的众多攻击中，维韦克·拉马斯瓦米 (Vivek Ramaswamy) 与尼基·黑利 (Nikki Haley) 之间的攻击最为严厉。拉马斯瓦米甚至在一场辩论中举起标语，指责这位南卡罗来纳州前州长兼联合国大使在她的公司工作中腐败，而她则进行了猛烈回击，称他不值得信任，并斥责他提及她的孩子。人身攻击在美国政治中司空见惯，黑莉和从未担任过民选公职的 38 岁企业家拉马斯瓦米都面临着从前总统唐纳德·特朗普手中夺取共和党提名的艰难过程。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 05:42:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/us-canada-news/indian-americans-rise-in-us-politics-navigate-identity/articleshow/106854535.cms</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争100天：白宫表示以色列缩减规模的“正确时机”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/white-house-says-its-the-right-time-for-israel-to-scale-back-gaza-war-as-fighting-hits-100-days/articleshow/106853883.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106853883.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;白宫国家安全委员会发言人约翰·柯比在哥伦比亚广播公司发表讲话时表示，美国一直在与以色列就加沙“向低强度行动过渡”进行对话。 “我们相信现在是进行过渡的正确时机。我们正在与他们讨论这样做，”他在“面对国家”节目中说道。这些评论暴露了战争第 100 天这两个亲密盟友之间日益扩大的分歧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 05:31:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/white-house-says-its-the-right-time-for-israel-to-scale-back-gaza-war-as-fighting-hits-100-days/articleshow/106853883.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列-哈马斯：战争会蔓延到真主党和“抵抗轴心”吗？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-hamas-will-war-spread-to-hezbollah-and-axis-of-resistance/articleshow/106853943.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106853943.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;布林肯对以色列的访问旨在缓和以色列与哈马斯战争中的中东紧张局势。然而，冲突可能会蔓延为涉及真主党的更广泛的战争。以色列对真主党日益好战，加上美国影响力的减弱，引发了人们的担忧。以色列国内针对被美国认定为恐怖组织的真主党的言论也变得更加好战。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 05:27:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-hamas-will-war-spread-to-hezbollah-and-axis-of-resistance/articleshow/106853943.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦：卡拉奇枪击事件造成四人受伤，其中包括记者</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-four-including-journalist-injured-in-firing-incidents-in-karachi/articleshow/106853843.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106853843.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据 ARY News 报道，周日在卡拉奇发生的多起枪击事件中，包括一名记者在内的四人受伤。肖阿布·伯尼 (Shoaib Burney) 是一家私人新闻频道的记者，当他在拉希德·米哈斯路 (Rashid Minhas Road) 行驶时，身份不明的袭击者向他的车辆开枪。在这三起案件中，武装袭击者都干净利落地逃跑了。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 05:21:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-four-including-journalist-injured-in-firing-incidents-in-karachi/articleshow/106853843.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国呼吁召开加沙和平会议，哈马斯披露以色列人质的命运</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/china-calls-for-gaza-peace-conference-hamas-to-disclose-fate-of-israeli-hostages/articleshow/106853364.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106853364.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国呼吁就加沙地带的以色列-哈马斯战争举行大规模、权威的和平会议，而该激进组织则播放了三名以色列人质的视频，并表示他们的命运将于周一公布。中国外交部长王毅周末在埃及发表讲话，呼吁“制定实施‘两国方案’的具体时间表和路线图。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 05:02:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/china-calls-for-gaza-peace-conference-hamas-to-disclose-fate-of-israeli-hostages/articleshow/106853364.cms</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜称试射高超音速导弹</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-korea-says-it-test-fired-hypersonic-missile/articleshow/106852681.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106852681.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;朝鲜周一表示，它成功试射了一枚装有高超音速机动弹头的新型弹道导弹。这次发射是平壤今年首次已知的武器试验，也是有史以来首次固体燃料高超音速中程弹道导弹（IRBM）试验，周日被首尔军方发现。朝鲜中央通讯社的一篇报道称，固体燃料IRMB“装载了高超音速机动控制弹头”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 04:41:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-korea-says-it-test-fired-hypersonic-missile/articleshow/106852681.cms</guid></item><item><title>“危及生命的冬季天气”：北极爆炸导致美国气温低于零度</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/life-threatening-winter-weather-all-you-need-to-know-about-arctic-blast-causing-below-zero-temperatures-in-us/articleshow/106852678.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106852678.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 04:45:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/life-threatening-winter-weather-all-you-need-to-know-about-arctic-blast-causing-below-zero-temperatures-in-us/articleshow/106852678.cms</guid></item><item><title>北极爆炸导致气温低于零，扰乱了美国各地的生活</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/arctic-blast-brings-below-zero-temperatures-and-disrupts-life-across-the-us/articleshow/106851317.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106851317.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;严重的北极风暴造成四人死亡，造成大范围停电，并扰乱了美国各地的日常生活。据估计，有 9500 万美国人因危险的低风寒而收到天气警报。气象学家警告称，可能会出现暴风雪天气，航空旅行将受到严重干扰。北极风暴预计将给阿肯色州、密西西比州北部和田纳西州西部的部分地区带来 4 至 6 英寸的降雪。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 03:58:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/arctic-blast-brings-below-zero-temperatures-and-disrupts-life-across-the-us/articleshow/106851317.cms</guid></item><item><title>文莱“性感”王子与平民结婚</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/bruneis-hot-prince-marries-commoner-in-grand-10-day-ceremony/articleshow/106850619.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106850619.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;这位 32 岁的王子是一名训练有素的直升机飞行员，是文莱皇家空军的少校，以马球运动成就、对老虎的喜爱以及 Instagram 上的大量粉丝而闻名，他与 29 岁的阿尼莎·罗斯纳·伊萨 (Anisha Rosnah Isa) 结婚了。非王室成员卡莱比奇参加了一场精心策划的为期 10 天的王室婚礼，婚礼于 1 月 7 日开始，将于 1 月 16 日结束。婚礼于 1 月 11 日在苏丹奥马尔·阿里·赛义夫丁清真寺正式合法化。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 03:35:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/bruneis-hot-prince-marries-commoner-in-grand-10-day-ceremony/articleshow/106850619.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国刺骨的寒冷考验着从德克萨斯州到阿尔伯塔省的电网</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/bone-chilling-cold-in-us-tests-power-grids-from-texas-to-alberta/articleshow/106849221.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106849221.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;德克萨斯州电力可靠性委员会在 2022 年 12 月的寒流期间创下了冬季需求记录，并预计在本周的冰冻期间挑战该记录。德克萨斯州受到特别关注，因为最近的寒潮是 2021 年 2 月以来罕见的冰冻天气之一。在那段时间，强烈的寒潮导致 200 多人死亡，并导致数百万人几天断电。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 03:02:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/bone-chilling-cold-in-us-tests-power-grids-from-texas-to-alberta/articleshow/106849221.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯发布令人不安的视频戏弄三名以色列人质的命运</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-hostages-hamas-video-noa-argamani-israel-hamas-war/articleshow/106848845.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106848845.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈马斯发布了令人毛骨悚然的视频，其中包括三名以色列人质：诺亚·阿加马尼、约西·沙拉比和伊泰·斯维尔斯基，他们在超新星狂欢袭击中被绑架。人质敦促以色列官员安全返回，而视频则警告他们命运不确定。诺亚·阿加马尼 (Noa Argamani) 的母亲正在与晚期脑癌作斗争，她向国际社会呼吁释放她的女儿。以色列军方表示，战争已进入新阶段。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 02:52:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-hostages-hamas-video-noa-argamani-israel-hamas-war/articleshow/106848845.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>